  <name>EdrawMax (unofficial)</name>
  <summary>All-in-one Diagram Software</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Multi-purpose diagram tool with a library of shapes and icons for almost any kind of info-graphic you might want to make. Useful for flow charts, electrical engineering, software planning, org charts etc.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please note that this is an unofficial effort by a third party to repackage the vendor's
      software for distribution via flatpak to offer more installation options, especially for
      those running immutable distros like Fedora Silverblue.
    </p>
  </description>

